#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
yoga-tray  v1.2
Combined system tray app for the Lenovo Yoga 9i Gen 7.

Right-click the tray icon to control:
  - Keyboard backlight  (off / dim / on / auto)
  - Performance profile (Power Saver / Balanced / Performance)
  - Refresh rate        (90 Hz / 60 Hz)
  - Key Bindings        (bind any Yoga special key to a preset or custom command)

The icon reflects the current performance profile and updates automatically
when the hardware performance key cycles the profile.

Requires: python3-gi
Optional: gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1 (better Cinnamon/Ubuntu tray integration)
          gir1.2-notify-0.7       (desktop notifications on state changes)
"""

